      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PROWESS (1) turned in a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 520m behind Bandit Lynne (30.73) in a Grade 5. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from five starts. Has ability and looks hard to stop. TROPIC SANDS (2) comes off an average effort last start when fifth at this track over 520m behind Snoopy's Ethics (30.78) in a Grade 5. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Likely to play a prominent role. SNEAKY TYCOON (3) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (34.98) in a Grade 5 at The Gardens. Solid record at the distance winning three races. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Expected to feature in the finish. FOLLOW THE ACE (4) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at his latest outing at this circuit.",
